{"tid":1289094,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"政府開始打溫情牌 香港人記得堅守訴求","createTime":"2019-07-06T02:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:24:59.000Z","uid":11374,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23771f267ddb349513d3a6482d4aeff830d0aeba","tid":1289094,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"依家日撚日都有局長出黎話會多聆聽<br />\n班撚屌硬既唔得開始出軟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明香港人既持續運動係有成效的</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家只要繼續keep住 長期抗爭<br />\n和理非就算唔衝擊  剩遊行都好 記得記得一定要出<br />\n只要人數夠多 亦可成為對前線戰友既一大支持<br />\n<br />\n香港都有自己既抗爭優勢 <br />\n一個好似香港咁既遊旅國際金融中心不繼keep住有抗爭運動  成效會有加剩<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續加油 堅守5大訴求<br />\n有遊行照出 有活動照出<br />\n要撐場照出 要關懷照出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">尋死tips撚果d就自己諗啦屌<br />\n乜野一個不能少 簡直係bullshit </span></span>"},{"pid":"c205f3ee569fd101ddb67086f1b339d3aa39fe3b","tid":1289094,"uid":120705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅守五大訴求，Bye政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ea9a093fda2134c3d17eae8855bc6ae297186973","tid":1289094,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3badb3ec032a87e2421555a65886a79c4e384a4f","tid":1289094,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bc45e95031b75b4cbfd442854df23cc18148dd","tid":1289094,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"大家唔好冷卻落黎<br />\n戰士付出太多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc1f51eccac559e00a273a708696103cec20a05","tid":1289094,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:25.0